	h2 Hard Rock Bali
	.story Upon arriving at the Gusti Ngurah Rai International Airport, we spotted the iconic black Hard Rock guitar sign. It stood out among a hundred white placards with names on it. Between the twenty minutes ride to the hotel, we laid eyes on blue waters of Kuta Beach. Upon check-in, Ellis went gaga over the decoration of flowers and chocolates. We had booked the "Naughty and Nice" package. They have other packages like Rock The House for families and Retune if you are into relaxing at the spa. The room decor was modern with a splash of bright colors. The Hard Rock logo was everywhere, starting from the bronze ring of guitars at the entrance down to the disposable bedroom slippers. If they had it their way, they probably stamp the logo on every guest's forehead too.
