	h2 Goodbye
	.story Hard Rock Bali was awesome from the start to the end. Although we only did the water sports, there is more Bali than that. We are saving those for until the next time. As our airplane flew off into the sunset, we saw Mount Bromo stuck its head out of the clouds and gave us a farewell.
